data.description:
Beautiful Contemporary Townhome in Littleton Village!!!! Move-in Ready, open floor plan with Stainless Appliances and Quartz Counters in the kitchen!!! Covered Patio that looks over the Park and Dog Park has one of the best locations for views!!! 9 ft.ceilings ,Large Master Berroom with on-suite Master Bath and Large walk-in Closet!!! Also a second really good size bedroom and full bathroom. Rooftop outdoor Patio with Gas Grill for entertaining Friends and Family and Fitness Center, complete this Luxury Condo!!!
Within walking distance to Starbucks, resturants and grocery stores. Convenient location and close to Park Meadows Mall, DTC, and C-470 AND I-25. 
THIS GORGEOUS CONDO IS PRICED TO SELL!!!
